	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The game's timing was altered so it would be the same speed in PAL as the NTSC version is in NTSC, but they apparently forgot to alter the demo code accordingly.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


